/tmp - short term storage, gets erase on boot
/var/tmp - same but doesnt get delete
/var/ - file that change often mail,logs,etc
/tmp - all user can write and delete all files

chmod o+t folder
chmode 1777 folder
chmode 0777 folder

set sticky bit, only user can delete

















































































































 





































 
